mestamp=209.0)\n      - [Deep dives into RAG subcategories](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=265.0)\n      - [Vector database security (replacing ASCII smuggling)](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=302.0)\n  - [Team to prioritize these 3 topics for next week](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=322.0)\n\n### Visual Content Challenges\n\n  - [Promptfoo requests breaking text with diagrams/images](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=394.0)\n  - [GrowthX can include references to existing internet resources](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=431.0)\n  - [Creating custom images/diagrams is challenging for GrowthX](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=454.0)\n  - [Exploring solutions:](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=468.0)\n      - [Repurposing existing content](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=530.0)\n      - [Using stock/AI-generated images with brand elements](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=540.0)\n      - [Potential future use of DataGrid's agentic AI for image identification](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=613.0)\n\n### Content Quality\n\n  - [Initial impression shows an increase in quality](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=369.0)\n  - [Detailed feedback pending after thorough review](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=364.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Vanessa to review articles this afternoon and provide comments](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=329.0)\n  - [Promptfoo to aim for posting a few articles this week](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=660.0)\n  - [GrowthX to prioritize and start work on the 3 approved new topics](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=322.0)\n  - [Explore solutions for including visual elements in articles](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=394.0)\n  - [Promptfoo to provide detailed feedback on content quality after review](https://fathom.video/share/2pbZXNvF8kakYB4s1LuV7fyFUeTZu3sS?tab=summary&timestamp=364.0)\n"
